    "longBusinessSummary": "Taseco Air Services Joint Stock Company, together with its subsidiaries, engages in airport commercial services in Vietnam. It operates through Sales of Goods and Rendering of Related Services in Terminals and Airports; and Hospitality and Catering Service segments. The company offers restaurants and mobile food services; travel agency, tour operator, and short stay services; road passenger transit; advertising services; telecommunication services; and other ancillary services. It also engages in the management of hotels; provision of catering services; pick-up and drop-off services; foreign currency exchange agents; retail of goods in general stores; and sale of souvenir products. The company was formerly known as Taseco Noi Bai Air Services Joint Stock Company and changed its name to Taseco Air Services Joint Stock Company in May 2017. The company is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam. Taseco Air Services Joint Stock Company is a subsidiary of Thang Long Air Services Corporation.",
